T1	Intervention 452 787	etoposide (50 mg/m(2) per day) administered orally as a single agent once or twice daily. On Day 8, patients started to receive dexamethasone, vincristine, and L-asparaginase. Etoposide was administered until Day 22. Two courses of consolidation therapy were followed by continuation therapy or hematopoietic stem cell transplantation.
